title: The Single Parent Resource Center's Fall Fete 2015 Honoring Alan Fuchsberg and the Junior League of the City of New York
desc: Please join us as we honor?Alan Fuchsberg and the Junior League of the City?of New York for their?dedication to?New York City's single parents and their families. All ticket sponsors at the Individual VIP Ticket level and above are entitled to attend a VIP tour of an exhibit, from 6:00-6:30 PM, donor recognition, and a listing as a benefit committee member, if purchased by October 7, 2015.? Please email Rosemarie Dackerman, Executive Director,?at  redackermansprc@aol.com , or call 212-951-7030, extension 239, if you would like to be listed as a benefit committee member. You may also mail your donation to: Rosemarie Dackerman, Executive Director, The Single Parent Resource Center 228 East 45th Street, 5th Floor New York, New York ?10017 ? The non tax-deductible component of each ticket is $55.00.
